erna]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Miami Fusion]]\n| '''10'''\n|- align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|BOL}} [[Jaime Moreno (footballer, born 1974)|Jaime Moreno]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[D.C. United]]\n| '''10'''\n|- align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|VEN}} [[Giovanni Savarese]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[New England Revolution]]\n| '''10'''\n|- align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Josh Wolff]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Chicago Fire S.C.|Chicago Fire]]\n| '''10'''\n|- align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"\n|\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|PAN}} [[Jorge Dely Vald\u00e9s]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Colorado Rapids]]\n| '''10'''\n|}\n\n==International Competition==\n\n[[CONCACAF Champions' Cup]]\n\n*'''[[Chicago Fire S.C.|Chicago Fire]]'''<br>Defeated {{flagicon|TRI}} [[Joe Public F.C.]] 2\u20130 (Quarterfinals).<br>Lost {{flagicon|CRC}} [[L.D. Alajuelense]] 5\u20134 PK, 1\u20131 draw (Semi-finals).<br>Draw {{flagicon|USA}} [[D.C. United]] Third place match 2\u20132. (Third place shared)\n*'''[[D.C. United]]'''<br>Defeated {{flagicon|HON}} [[Club Olimpia Deportivo|Olimpia]] 1\u20130 (Quarterfinals).<br>Lost {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Necaxa]] 3\u20131 (Semifinals).<br>Draw {{flagicon|USA}} [[Chicago Fire S.C.|Chicago Fire]] Third place match 2\u20132. (Third place shared)\n\n==Attendance==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%\";|\"text-align: center;\"\n!Club\n!Games\n!Home Total\n!Home Average\n|-\n|[[Columbus Crew]]\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|283,129\n|align=center|17,696\n|-\n|[[LA Galaxy|Los Angeles Galaxy]]\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|282,113\n|align=center|17,632\n|- \n|[[D.C. United]]\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|278,711\n|align=center|17,419\n|-\n|[[New England Revolution]]\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|267,752\n|align=center|16,795\n|-\n|[[Chicago Fire S.C.|Chicago Fire]]\n|align=center|16\n|align=center